This directory contains the updated version for our university assistant chatbot.

1) Files added:

actions/database.py

This python file contains code for retrieving information from web. Using beatifulsoup package three method were created: 

get_all_courses
get_courses_per_semester
get_course_information

The following urls were used in all methods and adjusted when necessary

URL_MAIN = 'https://www.di.uoa.gr'
URL_COURSES = "https://www.di.uoa.gr/en/studies/undergraduate/courses"

2) files updated:

a) actions.py

3 new costum actions were constructed:

action_list_courses
action_ask_course_name
action_give_course_info

b) nlu.yml 

Added 1 new intent that evokes the new action "action_list_courses":
- intent: request_list_of_courses_per_semester

Changed existing utterances and added new entities.
Changed names of some existing intents.

c) domain.yml

Added the three new actions.
Changed the names of intents to be aligned with nlu data

d) stories

Added new story "courses_list_path" 
Changed existing story "course_info_path"

